# AI Resume Maker Feature Extensions

This plan details the steps to implement Google Authentication, Notes Saver App, AI YouTube Summarizer, AI Job Search, Dashboard Sidebar updates, and Supabase Schema updates.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> Please review the proposed changes below. Once approved, I will begin execution.
> 
> Also, note that for features like Firecrawl, OpenRouter/Groq, and Google Auth, you will need to ensure the environment variables are set in [.env.local](file:///c:/Users/harsh/OneDrive/Desktop/AI_RESUME_MAKER/.env.local):
> - `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL`
> - `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`
> - `GROQ_API_KEY` (or `OPENROUTER_API_KEY`)
> - `FIRECRAWL_API_KEY`

## Proposed Changes

### Supabase Database
Summary: Add new tables and RLS policies for notes, youtube_summaries, and jobs_search_history.
#### [MODIFY] [supabase-schema.sql](file:///c:/Users/harsh/OneDrive/Desktop/AI_RESUME_MAKER/supabase-schema.sql)
- Add `notes` table (id, user_id, title, content, created_at)
- Add `youtube_summaries` table (id, user_id, video_url, summary, created_at)
- Add `jobs_search_history` table (id, user_id, role, location, results, created_at)
- Add Row Level Security (RLS) policies for user isolation.

---

### Authentication (Google OAuth)
Summary: Add Google OAuth login/signup buttons and update the Navbar.
#### [MODIFY] [login/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/harsh/OneDrive/Desktop/AI_RESUME_MAKER/src/app/(auth)/login/page.tsx)
- Add "Continue with Google" button calling `supabase.auth.signInWithOAuth({ provider: 'google' })`.
#### [MODIFY] [signup/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/harsh/OneDrive/Desktop/AI_RESUME_MAKER/src/app/(auth)/signup/page.tsx)
- Add "Continue with Google" button.
#### [MODIFY] [navbar.tsx](file:///c:/Users/harsh/OneDrive/Desktop/AI_RESUME_MAKER/src/components/shared/navbar.tsx)
