## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Validate TypeScript build with `npm run build` once implementation is complete.
- Ensure ESLint passes using `npm run lint`.

### Manual Verification
1. I will deploy the Supabase schema changes using standard Supabase dashboard queries (the user needs to do this on their end with the provided SQL).
2. Start the local server via `npm run dev`.
3. Verify that the user can login with Google.
4. Go to `/notes` and ensure creating/deleting a note works and persists.
5. Go to `/youtube-summary`, paste a video, and test AI summary output.
6. Go to `/ai-job-search`, enter "Software Engineer", and check the Firecrawl + LLM result.
